::  gen/sovnas/configure: set sovnas storage root path and max file size
::
::  Usage from dojo:
::    :sovnas &sovnas-action [%set-config /home/nativeplanet/sovnas 524.288.000 %.n]
::
::  This generator just prints a reminder of the poke syntax.
::
:-  %say
|=  [[now=@da eny=@ud bek=beak] ~ ~]
:-  %tang
:~  leaf+"To configure sovnas, run from dojo:"
    leaf+":sovnas &sovnas-action [%set-config /home/nativeplanet/sovnas 524.288.000 %.n]"
==
